               <p>(The witnesses were examined apart at the request of the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17740216-68-person579">
                  James
                   Ferguson
               <interp inst="t17740216-68-person579" type="surname" value="Ferguson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17740216-68-person579" type="given" value="James"></interp>
