                     <interp inst="t17740216-68-person593" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known him fell greens; his mother keeps a green-stall in Duke's-Place ; he has bore a good character; I know no harm of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17740216-68-person594">
                  Joseph
                   Lyons
               <interp inst="t17740216-68-person594" type="surname" value="Lyons"></interp>
