               <p>Q. to Aaron. What is the prisoner's name?</p>
               <p>Aaron. I know him by the name of Abraham; I do not know him by the nick-name Levy talked of, that he was more commonly called by; his father is called 
               <persName id="t17740216-68-person595">
                  Abraham
               <interp inst="t17740216-68-person595" type="given" value="Abraham"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17740216-68-person595" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             the green man, because he sold greens: I never knew any harm of him.</p>
